==French==
===Etymology===
Old French [[gaignier]], from Old Frankish ''*waidanjan'' ‘get food’, a calque of Latin [[petere]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/gaɲe/}}

===Verb===
'''gagner'''
# To [[win]]
#:''On a gagné la ligue!.''
#::''We won the league.''
# To [[earn]]
#:''Je gagne 10 euros par heure.''
#::''I earn 10 euros an hour.''

===Conjugation===
{{fr-conj-er|gagn|avoir}}

